<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.4">
<l>tēṉukaṉ pilampaṉ kāḷiya ṉeṉṉum</l>
<l rend="indent">tīppap pūṭuka ḷaṭaṅkavu ḻakki</l>
<l>kāṉakam paṭiyu lāviyu lāvik</l>
<l rend="indent">karuñciṟuk kaṉkuḻa lūtiṉa pōtu</l>
<l>mēṉakai yoṭuti lōttamai yarampai</l>
<l rend="indent">yuruppaci yaravar veḷkima yaṅki</l>
<l>vāṉakam paṭiyil vāytiṟap piṉṟi</l>
<l rend="indent">yāṭalpā ṭalavai māṟiṉar tāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the dark lad played [his] flute</l>
<l rend="indent">while walking about in the forest,</l>
<l rend="indent">crushing and trampling the scorched weeds</l>
<l rend="indent">called Dhenuka, Pralamba, and Kāliya,</l>
<l>on earth and in heaven,</l>
<l>Menakā, Tilottamā, Urvaśī, Rambhā and [the other] Apsaras,</l>
<l rend="indent">shy and bewildered,</l>
<l rend="indent">without [even] opening [their] mouths,</l>
<l>ceased singing and dancing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
